mandatory.cftc_obligation:
CFTC must: (1) establish process for submitting all significant regulatory actions to OIRA before publication; 
(2) Chairman Selig must establish regular consultation schedule with OMB, DPC, and NEC directors; 
(3) create and fill a GS-15 White House Liaison position in Schedule C excepted service; 
(4) submit strategic plans to OMB for clearance before finalization; 
(5) comply with OMB performance standards and management objectives.
